# Combine HTML Files Plan

## Goal Description
Combine [example1.html](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/School/10th-grade/APCSA/untitled1/src/example1.html) through [example6.html](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/School/10th-grade/APCSA/untitled1/src/example6.html) into a single HTML file. The content within the `<body>` tags of the source files will be extracted and interleaved/shuffled to "mess up the order a little bit" while ensuring the resulting HTML is still syntactically correct (valid tags, proper nesting).

